  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      - To investigate the safety of letrozole monotherapy at a dose 1.0 mg/day or fadrozole
      monotherapy at a dose 2.0mg in Japanese postmenopausal patients with advanced breast cancer
      which participated in double blind study.
    </textblock>
